data.description: Looking for space East of Redding ? Only 20 minutes to Palo Cedro ! Great schools, with bus stops close by. Fully fenced 10 acres right by the country store and fire station.Set up for horse enthusiasts with full solar electric fencing and horse panels.  Never worry about water! Newer 300 ft well and filtration system and central heating and air. Chicken coop, above ground pool and large shop for the hobbies, plenty of producing fruit trees, plus a shared pond ! Behind the property are tons of riding trails!  Large bedrooms, one downstairs and new flooring. Rustic touches, and a paint credit for your taste, and solar to top it off! Looking for a homestead that has it all? Here you go !
